OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMcIlwaine 34, from Hazel Close,
OL,8,FLagmore, in west Belfast, was found
OL,9,Fguilty by a jury in October of the
OL,10,Fmurder of James Joseph Crossley, 38,
OL,11,Fat her former home in March 2022.
OL,13,FDuring a sentencing hearing at Belfast
OL,14,FCrown Court on Thursday, Mr Justice
OL,15,FKinney heard submissions ahead of
OL,16,Fsetting a tariff for how long she
OL,17,Fwould spend in prison.
