OL,7,FProsecuting barrister Richard Weir KC
OL,8,Ftold the court there had been an
OL,9,Fargument between McIlwaine and her
OL,10,Fpartner on the day of his death.
OL,12,FHe said: "We say the defendant chose
OL,13,Fto kill James Crossley rather than to
OL,14,Ffollow any other options before her.
OL,15,FShe killed him when he was asleep.
