OL,4,Cslept in 'premeditated' murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"She went from the top bedroom to the
OL,8,Fkitchen, she selected what appears to
OL,9,Fhave been the largest knife and
OL,10,Freturned to the bedroom and stabbed
OL,11,Fhim multiple times with the intention
OL,12,Fof killing him."
OL,14,FThe barrister said it was not a
OL,15,Fborderline case between murder and
OL,16,Fmanslaughter.
OL,18,FHe added: "It was premeditated,
OL,19,Fplanned and the intention was to kill
OL,20,Fand nothing else."
