OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FDefence barrister Eilis McDermott KC
OL,8,Ftold the court that McIlwaine had a
OL,9,Fhigh degree of regret for her actions.
OL,11,FShe said: "The reality is that the
OL,12,Fdefendant was the victim of a
OL,13,Fsignificant level of domestic violence
OL,14,Fand coercive control over a protracted
OL,15,Fperiod."
OL,17,FThe barrister told the court the case
OL,18,Fcame "close to the borderline" between
OL,19,Fmurder and manslaughter.
